          <title>BYU wins last second thriller over Oklahoma State, 38-35</title>
          <description><![CDATA[PROVO, Utah (ABC4 Sports) - The dream season for BYU continues. Jake Retzlaff threw a 35-yard touchdown pass to Darius Lassiter with 10 seconds left and No. 13 BYU remained undefeated, outlasting Oklahoma State 38-35 on Friday night.]]></description>
