          <title>Tom Brady's purchase of a minority stake in the Las Vegas Raiders approved by NFL team owners</title>
          <description><![CDATA[ATLANTA (AP) — Tom Brady has another new role in the NFL: owner. The seven-time Super Bowl champion purchased a minority stake in the Las Vegas Raiders, a deal unanimously approved by NFL team owners on Tuesday at the league's annual fall meeting.]]></description>
